    <objectives>
      <material>
        <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;h1&gt;Session 9 Quiz – Inheritance and Method Overriding&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test your understanding of class inheritance, extends keyword, super, and method overriding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Topics Covered:&lt;/strong&gt;
- extends keyword and inheritance
- super() in constructors
- super.method() calls
- Method overriding
- Parent and child classes
- Inheritance patterns&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions:&lt;/strong&gt;
- 16 questions from the Session 9 question bank
- 20 minute time limit
- 3 attempts allowed
- 16 points total (1 point per question)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;After syncing the question bank to Canvas:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</mattext>
      </material>
    </objectives>
